    if name in local:

    globals()[name]+=1
    aux = globals()[name]

    #Equivalent to name++
    if name in local: # uncovered
        local[name]+=1 # uncovered
        aux = local[name]-1 # uncovered
        return aux # uncovered
    globals()[name]+=1
    aux = globals()[name]-1
    return aux # uncovered

a = 1
b = PostIncrement('a') #b is 1 and a is 2

x = 1
